      <title>税收、关税等：美国大选的五大关键经济利害关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/us-election-5-economic-impacts-include-taxes-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二的美国大选将产生深远的经济影响，从美国人如何纳税到美国如何与世界其他国家进行贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/us-election-5-economic-impacts-include-taxes-immigration</guid>
